The API for factory.contextExpression and factory.matchExpression are not consistent. That is, context expression takes: contextExpression(Class<T> elementClass, IExpression expr, Object... parameters);
whereas, match expression takes: matchExpression(IExpression expression, Object... parameters);
(notice the missing elementClass parameter).
However, when you actually create the query, the MatchQuery takes the element class, whereas the QLContextQuery doesn't.
Can / should these be made consistent?

